info.author: Jonathan Merritt
info.description:
A set of megawidgets based upon the PyGTK GUI library for 
Python that provide strip charting capabilities for displaying 
data that is sampled periodically.
info.name: pystripchart
info.platform: python + PyGTK (tested under Linux and Solaris only!)
info.summary: Strip chart megawidgets built on top of PyGTK
